00:00:34.239 --> 00:00:37.186
that we've seen in the past,
it does seem to have a pattern.

00:00:37.186 --> 00:00:39.682
For example, if this said x squared

00:00:39.682 --> 00:00:43.361
plus eight x plus seven,

00:00:43.361 --> 00:00:44.940
you'd say, oh, well, this
is pretty straightforward

00:00:44.940 --> 00:00:45.839
