00:00:45.839 --> 00:00:47.532
What two numbers add up to eight

00:00:47.532 --> 00:00:49.251
and when I take their product I get seven?

00:00:49.251 --> 00:00:51.677
Well, there's only two numbers
where you take their product

00:00:51.677 --> 00:00:54.138
