00:00:56.936 --> 00:00:59.594
add up to positive eight,
and that's one and seven.

00:00:59.594 --> 00:01:02.009
So this would be x plus seven

00:01:02.009 --> 00:01:05.387
times x plus one.

00:01:05.387 --> 00:01:07.036
Well, if you just think of,

00:01:07.036 --> 00:01:09.520
instead of thinking in
terms of x and x squared,

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:10.901
if you just think in terms of x squared

00:01:10.901 --> 00:01:11.958
and x to the fourth, it's going to be

00:01:11.958 --> 00:01:13.339
the exact same thing.

00:01:13.339 --> 00:01:15.440
So this thing can be written as

00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:18.018
