plus eight a plus seven,

00:01:38.585 --> 00:01:41.464
and then you would factor this into

00:01:41.464 --> 00:01:45.364
a plus seven and a plus one,

00:01:45.364 --> 00:01:48.023
and then you would undo the substitution,

00:01:48.023 --> 00:01:49.439
and that's x squared plus seven

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:50.584
and x squared plus one.

00:01:50.584 --> 00:01:52.105
But hopefully you see
what's going on here;

00:01:52.105 --> 00:01:55.402
