00:01:59.732 --> 00:02:01.032
And so you could do a substitution,

00:02:01.032 --> 00:02:02.368
or you could just recognize, oh okay,

00:02:02.368 --> 00:02:04.689
instead of dealing with x squared,

00:02:04.689 --> 00:02:06.895
I'm dealing with x to the fourth.

00:02:06.895 --> 00:02:09.147
All right, so that's the numerator.

