I don't see an x to the fourth minus one,

00:02:39.783 --> 00:02:41.567
or a three x in the numerator,

00:02:41.567 --> 00:02:43.645
but maybe I can factor this out further,

00:02:43.645 --> 00:02:45.294
x to the fourth minus one.

00:02:45.294 --> 00:02:48.254
And that's because it is
