Well, this would be a squared minus one

00:03:01.326 --> 00:03:05.749
if you say that a is equal to x squared.

00:03:05.749 --> 00:03:08.349
Then this would be a squared minus one.

00:03:08.349 --> 00:03:10.404
So let's rewrite all of this.

00:03:10.404 --> 00:03:12.273
So let's rewrite.

