00:04:29.066 --> 00:04:32.467
Positive or negative one
would make this expression

00:04:32.467 --> 00:04:33.802
right over here equal zero,

00:04:33.802 --> 00:04:35.439
so it cannot be equal to zero,

00:04:35.439 --> 00:04:38.818
x cannot be equal to, I'll
write plus or minus one;

00:04:38.818 --> 00:04:40.721
